odescubrimiento%20continuo%2C%20examinarnos%20a%20nosotros%C2%A0mismos%20nos%20permite%20tener%20plena%20conciencia%20de%20los%20conflictos%20de%20car%C3%A1cter%2C%C2%A0miedos%2C%20incomodidades%2C%20inseguridades%20y%20limitaciones%3B%20y%20es%20ah%C3%AD%20donde%20se%C2%A0encuentran%20nuestras%20%C3%A1reas%20de%20oportunidad%20y%20expansi%C3%B3n%2C%20para%20liberar%20al%C2%A0verdadero%20ser%20que%20tenemos%20dentro%2C%20el%20magn%C3%ADfi%20co%20ser%20que%20puede%20llegar%20a%20otro%C2%A0nivel%20de%20crecimiento%2C%20para%20culminar%20en%20la%20cima%20monta%C3%B1osa.%0D%0ANos%20sanamos%20permitiendo%20el%20flujo%20y%20la%C2%A0expresi%C3%B3n%20de%20nuestros%20sentimientos%2C%C2%A0sin%20necesidad%20de%20lastimar%20u%20ofender%20a%C2%A0otros%2C%20con%20la%20finalidad%20de%20reconocer%20lo%C2%A0que%20en%20realidad%20sentimos%20y%20pensamos%3B%C2%A0al%20expresarlo%2C%20desahogamos%20todo%20lo%C2%A0que%20hay%20en%20nuestro%20interior%20y%20siempre%C2%A0acompa%C3%B1ados%20nos%20sentimos%2C%20cuando%C2%A0elijamos%20a%20alguien%20que%20sabemos%20nos%C2%A0comprender%C3%A1%20y%20empat%C3%ADa%20brindar%C3%A1.%0D%0ANos%20sanamos%2C%20por%20supuesto%2C%20viviendo%C2%A0el%20valor%20del%20perd%C3%B3n%2C%20brind%C3%A1ndolo%20a%20los%C2%A0dem%C3%A1s%20y%20a%20nosotros%20mismos.%0D%0APor%20otra%20parte%2C%20un%20concepto%20muy%C2%A0interesante%20alrededor%20de%20este%20tema%20es%C2%A0la%20%E2%80%9Ccatarsis%E2%80%9D%2C%20la%20cual%20es%20un%20proceso%20de%C2%A0purificaci%C3%B3n%20a%20nivel%20corporal%2C%20emocional%2C%C2%A0espiritual%20y%20mental%3B%20una%20forma%20de%C2%A0limpiar%20el%20alma.%20La%20palabra%20proviene%20del%C2%A0t%C3%A9rmino%20griego%20k%C3%A1tharsis%2C%20que%20significa%C2%A0purificaci%C3%B3n.%0D%0AY%20es%20%28catarsis%29%20la%20expresi%C3%B3n%20de%20las%C2%A0emociones%20ligadas%20a%20un%20recuerdo%20o%20trauma%2C%0D%0Agenerando%20un%20desbloqueo%20de%20la%20emoci%C3%B3n%20o%C2%A0del%20recuerdo%2C%20permitiendo%20a%20la%20persona%0D%0Aentenderlas%20y%20poder%20expres